quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Naboola mbu: “ Murumilwe shina enywe Abarumwa ? ”"
  51,32,"Nibabola mbu: “ toto efwe khurumilwe khubandu abetsimbi.”"
  51,33,Khubalasile amachino keliloba
  51,34,Karebwakhwo eshimanyisio okhurula khu Nyasaye wo khulwa balia babura eshichelo
  51,35,Ne nikhurusiamwo Abasuubili balimwo
  51,36,Ne shikhwanyoolamwo halali inzu ndala yonyene yabasuubili
  51,37,Ne nikhulekhamwo eshimanyisio khubalia baritsanga eshinyasio eshilulu
  51,38,"Ne khulukano lwa Musa, olwa khwamuruma khu Firauni nende ebifune bilolekha"
  51,39,"Nakhola obufuru khumaanikeke naboola mbu, “ Oli Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,40,Nenikhumutila nende omukanda kukwe kwabalwani nikhubasukuna munyanza naye nali ufunaanibwa
  51,41,"Ne (ukhusishibwa khwa) Abandu ba A’aad, olwa khwabarumila omuyeka omukumba"
  51,42,Shikwalekha shiosi shosi shiakwaburakhwo halali nikushikhola shinga likoshe
  51,43,"Ne Abandu ba Thsamudi, Olwa baboolelwa mbu: “ Musangale / mwikhoye khubise bititi”"
  51,44,"Ne nibakhaya okhulonda amalako ka Nyasaye wabu, mana likulu nilibakhupa nabo nibalola"
  51,45,Mana nibakhaywa okhwema ne nibalanyalilwa akhwihabina tawe
  51,46,"Ne Abandu ba Nuh imbeli eyo, toto bali Abandu aboononi"
  51,47,"Ne likulu khwaliumbakha khumaani nende obunyali, ne toto efwe khuli nobunyali obushila ako"
  51,48,"Ne liloba khwaliala, ne khuli abaali abalayi balibarie efwe"
  51,49,Ne buli eshindu khwaloonga eshisaatsa neshikhasi kho munyoole okhwitsulila
  51,50,"Mwilushile ewa Nyasaye, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wenyu owahabulafu"
  51,51,"Ne mulameta khu Nyasaye, nyasaye wundi tawe, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wahabulafu urula khuye"
  51,52,"Ne endio,shiyabetsela Omurumwa yesi yesi khubali imbeli wabu halali baboola mbu: “Oyo ni Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,53,Ne koo baboolanila kano? halali bo ni Abandu abakhayi
  51,54,"Mana lekhana ninabo, nawe sholafunanibwa tawe"
  51,55,"Ne itsulisia, toto ametsulisio kakhoonyanga Abasuubili"
  51,56,Ne shindaloonga Majini nende Abandu halali khulwokhunaama esie
  51,57,"Ne Shebenyakhwo omukabo tawe, ne shindenya bandisie tawe"
  51,58,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omukabi, Owamani amanji"
  51,59,"Ne toto balia abamabii, bali nende tsimbi tsiabu shinga tsimbi tsia abaashiabwe. kho balayungubasia tawe"
  51,60,Ne eshinyasio eshikhongo khubalia bakhaya inyanga yabu yabalakwa
  52,1,Nditsuba khulukulu lwa Tur
  52,2,Nende khushitabu shiahandikwa
  52,3,Khuliseelo liabambulwa
  52,4,Nende khunzu yombakhwa
  52,5,Nende khushitsafu shiachingulwa
  52,6,Nende khunyanza yetsula
  52,7,Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shilibaho
  52,8,Abulaho ulishikalila
  52,9,Inyanga yelikulu lilirenga okhurenga khwene
  52,10,Ne tsingulu lwatsilikulukha bukulukha
  52,11,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubayingani
  52,12,Balia babayanga mumakhuwa kobusilu
  52,13,Inyanga yabaliluumwa mumulilo obutinyu
  52,14,"Baliboolewa mbu: “Kuno niko omulilo kwa mwaingananga.”"
  52,15,Koo buno ni obulosi nohomba shimulolangasa tawe
  52,16,"Injilemwo, mwifwile nohomba mukhaye okhwifwila ninashilala, toto enywe murungungwa kamwakholanga"
  52,17,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende mubwokholo
  52,18,"Nibasangalila khuka Nyasaye wabu abahele, ne Nyasaye wabu alibahonokosia khu shinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,19,Lie ne munywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga
  52,20,"Ne baliyekha khubifumbi bwoluyali, bilondokhane khulunyaali, ne khulibabashila Abakhana bomwikulu (Hurul ain)"
  52,21,"Ne balia basuubila mana olwibulo lwabu nilubaloonda khukhusuubila khulibabukanania, ne shikhulibalemilia khubikhole biabu shiosishiosi tawe, buli Omundu alirungwa shiayakhola"
  52,22,Ne khulibametela buli imbia yebiamo nende yeyinyama shingala benya
  52,23,Balihelesaniamwo tsigilasi tsilimwo eshinywebwa shibulamwo eshifwabi nohomba obwonooni